Quantity Takeoffs

Accurate Earthwork & Material Calculations

Professional AGTEK Takeoffs

Get accurate quantities to bid confidently and win more work

Using industry-leading AGTEK software, we calculate cut/fill volumes, material quantities, and underground utilities so you know exactly what you're bidding on—no surprises, no guesswork. Our detailed takeoffs help you identify project scope, understand site challenges, and submit winning bids with confidence.

What We Calculate:

Earthwork Volumes

Cut/fill quantities, mass haul analysis, and topsoil stripping calculations for balanced site work

Material Quantities

Asphalt tonnage, concrete volumes, aggregate base, and all finished surface areas

Underground Utilities

Trench volumes, bedding requirements, backfill quantities, and pipe/fitting counts

Specialized Analysis

Rock excavation quantities, demolition volumes, and phased construction breakdowns

Our Process:

  • Complete plan review and scope verification
  • Detailed digitization of all surfaces and features
  • Accurate volume calculations with AGTEK software
  • Material quantity breakdowns by area or phase
  • Comprehensive reports with visual documentation
  • Quick turnaround to meet bid deadlines

What You Get:

Detailed Reports

Complete quantity breakdowns with supporting calculations and visual aids

Fast Turnaround

Most takeoffs completed within 24-48 hours to meet your bid deadlines

Expert Support

Direct access to takeoff specialists who understand your bidding needs

Revision Tracking

Clear documentation of plan changes and quantity adjustments

Fast turnaround • Competitive pricing

Why Accurate Takeoffs Matter

Bad quantities kill profits. Underestimate and you absorb the cost overruns. Overestimate and you lose the bid. That's why contractors trust our AGTEK-powered takeoffs for their most important projects.

With over hundreds of projects completed, we've helped contractors bid smarter, reduce risk, and win more profitable work. Our thorough approach catches details others miss, giving you the competitive edge you need in today's market.

View Our Pricing

Transparent, project-based pricing with no surprises.

Questions?

Talk directly with a takeoff specialist.
